article.description: — Terry Taylor had 25 points and 16 rebounds as Austin Peay edged past East Tennessee State 67-66 on Thursday.
article.headline: Taylor carries Austin Peay past East Tennessee State 67-66
article.linkText: Taylor carries Austin Peay past East Tennessee State 67-66
article.story: ESTERO, Fla. -- — Terry Taylor had 25 points and 16 rebounds as Austin Peay edged past East Tennessee State 67-66 on Thursday. Reginald Gee had 11 points and Mike Peake added eight rebounds for Austin Peay (2-0). Taylor put back his own miss with 4.8 seconds left for the go-ahead basket. Ledarrius Brewer had 16 points for the Buccaneers (0-2). Ty Brewer added 14 points and Vonnie Patterson had eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
